videos.headline: Fink escapes sack on 31-yard TD pass
videos.description: Matt Fink avoids the Utah pressure and connects with Amon-Ra St. Brown in the end zone for a USC touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fink escapes sack on 31-yard TD pass) 2019/09/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pittman hauls in 78-yard TD
videos.description: Matt Fink throws a deep ball to Michael Pittman Jr. who fights off two Utah defenders for the USC touchdown.

videos.headline: Fink leads USC to upset of Utah with 3 TDs
videos.description: After QB Kedon Slovis exits early after taking a big hit, QB Matt Fink comes in and tosses three touchdowns to lead USC to an upset of undefeated Utah.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Fink leads USC to upset of Utah with 3 TDs) 2019/09/20 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Fink honored USC coach let him play after trying to transfer
videos.description: Matt Fink says he is grateful to have an opportunity to play for USC after entering the transfer portal before the season.
